        </p>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 20px font-family: Calibri;font-size: 11px;"><strong> Leachable Study on Drug products </strong></div>
        <p style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 11px;">
            The Leachable profile for a Drug Product will be generated using essentially similar methods used in the Extractable study of the corresponding CCS. 
        </p>
        <p style="font-family: Calibri;font-size: 11px;">
